{"tid":1624733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想贏嘅話 有樣嘢唔做唔得","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:49:18.000Z","uid":232728,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d68989a2213ff392a3bb0d56af4e87d9a09e9742","tid":1624733,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:43:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係文宣呀</span></strong></span><br />\n小弟見到有唔少po都講無論係外國定本土都有唔少人唔知我地做呢樣做嗰樣嘅原因 而自己出街都聽到唔少長輩話點解班後生要咁樣做 點解班後生又要咁樣做 咁即係代表咩呀？<br />\n即係代表我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣不足呀</span></span><br />\n如果你決定今日去組團裝修嘅 請萬事小心 請記住不受傷不被捕嘅原則<br />\n如果唔想裝修嘅 可以留係屋企上網去做文宣 Twitter又好Facebook又好 乜都好 一定唔可以只留係連登 除咗留係屋企上網打鍵戰 可以嘅話可以去連儂牆貼下文宣或者係屋企樓下貼都得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港人 反抗</div></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8a12afb402b9bac43779fac8989dcf72cd22c67a","tid":1624733,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:46:00.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"9b689717508e4ad97f32c38824eec3d8fd31aec5","tid":1624733,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:46:13.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"2844eb668e4109fec5ae9ee27f938732ca16baec","tid":1624733,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:46:26.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"f6dff23198172c9e382d2b910350c3e8c4885ce8","tid":1624733,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"自推 4/10"},{"pid":"6a28e9714c3b7259ba0463711b5c958b6f83d771","tid":1624733,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:47:39.000Z","msg":"幫手推呀 唔好只係正評呀"},{"pid":"fe566d6e7bed38176edb3c679dfa889fd90922be","tid":1624733,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:49:18.000Z","msg":"自推5/1